	<p style="margin-bottom: 0.14in; text-align: justify;">Borghi S.p.A. offers&nbsp;<a href="/products/2013-09-27-11-27-50/search-by-machine">machinery for the broom and brush industry,</a><br /> ensuring its customers over 65 years of experience, state-of-the-art technology and utmost professionalism in service.<br />The <a href="/about-us/company">flexibility and versatility,</a> combined with the <a href="/about-us/certifications">quality and reliability of Borghi products</a><a href="/azienda/azienda"> </a>are the factors for growth and success. Borghi’s product range is complete: all kinds of machines for the production of brooms, brushes, strip brushes and mops, covering every segment of the Brush Industry, from <a href="/k2-styles-2/filling-machines-household">household items</a> to the most specialized of <a href="/k2-styles-2/filling-machines-technical-industrial/itemlist/category/58">technical and industrial brushes</a>. <a href="/about-us/company">[...]</a></p></div>
